---
description: Shared data contract and Supabase guidance
globs:
  - "src/lib/env.ts"
  - "src/lib/supabase/**"
  - "src/data/**"
  - "src/features/shared/**"
alwaysApply: false
---

- This area owns shared schemas, backend contracts, and Supabase access patterns.
- Do not hardcode secrets or fake env fallbacks.
- Missing Supabase env is a valid local shell state; fail only when a backend-dependent flow is used.
- Prefer central typed contracts over duplicated request or response shapes.
